.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: purple, lilac, blood-red, mauve, amber
There are 5 different nationalities: american, mexican, turkish, malaysian, russian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-cola, almond-milk, cola, sprite
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: purplemaster, baccarat, bongani, chaman, vegafina
5 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle, goldpony, pony, goat
1. the american is the person who likes blood-red
2. the swedish is the owner of the goldpony
3. the mexican is the person drinking cola
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes mauve
5. the person who likes lilac is the person drinking iced-cola
6. the bongani-smoker is the owner of the turtle
7. the person who likes amber is the baccarat-smoker
8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle
9. the malaysian is on the far left
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster
11. the owner of the goats is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker
12. the purplemaster-smoker is the person drinking juice
13. the turkish is the chaman-smoker
14. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person who likes purple
15. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    amber	|     purple	|      blood-red	|     lilac	|     mauve	|
| Nationality	|   malaysian	|    mexican	|    american	|    turkish	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     hamster	|    goat	|     turtle	|     pony	|      goldpony	|
| Beverage	|    sprite	|     cola	|     almond-milk	|    iced-cola	|      juice	|
| Cigar		|   baccarat	|    vegafina	|  bongani	|    chaman	|   purplemaster	|
